about.summary: Helper functions for runtime type checking

name: typechecks
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "typechecks" %}
{% set version = "0.1.0" %}
{% set sha256 = "7d801a6018f60d2a10aa3debc3af65f590c96c455de67159f39b9b183107c83b" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed .

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - pip
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - typechecks

about:
  home: https://github.com/openvax/typechecks
  license: Apache-2.0
  summary: 'Helper functions for runtime type checking'
  license_family: Apache
  license_file: '{{ environ["RECIPE_DIR"] }}/LICENSE'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - npavlovikj
